						<summary>

						<p>Pillar set up in front of a <hi rend="italic">Liṅga</hi> in a field to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>This undated epigraph may be assigned to the 17th century, on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It contains an invocation to Ghaṇṭākarṇa to ward off the hoof-disease in cattle.</p>						

						</summary>
